item.description:
&ldquo;Communism failed in real life because humans like to own things.&rdquo;
-Anonymous
 I was in a high-profile marriage once. My father was working with a builder and was invited to his son&rsquo;s wedding. I accompanied him to the place because I was curious. Unlike middle-class weddings, they had their guests sitting in small groups in separate lavish rooms while a separate receptionist catered to each. A beautiful place. People wearing their best.
